1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,490
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,490 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 11

3
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:42,680
Bravo!

4
00:01:42,729 --> 00:01:43,940
Bravo!

5
00:01:44,710 --> 00:01:47,560
Bravo! Bravo!

6
00:01:47,570 --> 00:01:49,780
Bravo! Bravo!

7
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:51,680
I said that the performers are all indecent.

8
00:01:51,690 --> 00:01:53,150
Mr. Cheng said that I’m inflexible.

9
00:01:53,690 --> 00:01:55,220
After seeing this,

10
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:56,620
though I can’t judge other performers,

11
00:01:56,630 --> 00:01:58,150
I’m sure that the Zhou on the stage

12
00:01:58,490 --> 00:02:00,740
is not a decent lady.

13
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,550
Sis, this is

14
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,600
a performance.

15
00:02:09,570 --> 00:02:10,910
But he

16
00:02:11,350 --> 00:02:13,320
performs such

17
00:02:13,330 --> 00:02:14,470
a sultry woman well.

18
00:02:14,950 --> 00:02:17,240
He won’t be good in real life.

19
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:20,070
Arts are from life.

20
00:02:20,370 --> 00:02:22,980
His real character is shown on the stage.

21
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:24,300
You know nothing.

22
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:25,840
A good performer

23
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:27,480
plays every role vividly.

24
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:34,040
Sis, you didn’t watch Ruan Lingyu’s movies.

25
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:36,060
She’s a decent lady

26
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:39,520
but she played the harlot well.

27
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,570
Chunxing. Mind your manner.

28
00:02:44,579 --> 00:02:47,360
Mrs. Cheng, when I was in the water room...

29
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,079
Mrs. Cheng.

30
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:00,240
Nice.

31
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:02,000
What a theater.

32
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:04,740
The shows are both on and off the stage.

33
00:03:06,270 --> 00:03:06,960
Go home.

34
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,920
Sis, there’s still another show.

35
00:03:10,350 --> 00:03:12,120
I’m enough with the shows here.

36
00:03:12,270 --> 00:03:14,060
Go. Give them the reward.

37
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:17,340
Wait.

38
00:03:19,990 --> 00:03:22,540
Mr. Shang is a good actor

39
00:03:22,829 --> 00:03:24,960
who plays Zou well.

40
00:03:25,070 --> 00:03:26,460
This is what he deserves.

41
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:28,860
Tell me

42
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,430
when he plays Ms. Wang,

43
00:03:30,850 --> 00:03:32,140
the old lady who incites

44
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:34,079
Pan Jinlian to seduce Ximen Qing,

45
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:36,510
I’ll come to watch. Go.

46
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:38,470
But...

47
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:40,230
Sis! Sis!

48
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:44,200
What?

49
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,440
I went out today.

50
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,720
Peking isn’t warmer than the northeast.

51
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:07,160
The packmen were selling frozen persimmons.

52
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:13,000
Don’t you care where I went?

53
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:18,180
Today...

54
00:04:20,230 --> 00:04:21,579
Today...

55
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,260
I had many things.

56
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:28,520
Let’s talk about this tomorrow.

57
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,080
Where did you have fun?

58
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:32,620
Did you watch

59
00:04:32,630 --> 00:04:34,880
the opera as well?

60
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,590
A rumor in Shuiyun Theater,

61
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,700
says that you don’t match Mr. Cheng.

62
00:04:54,850 --> 00:04:56,740
The performers discussed how to seduce him

63
00:04:56,780 --> 00:04:58,270
and take place of you.

64
00:05:05,650 --> 00:05:06,980
Shang Xirui,

65
00:05:07,410 --> 00:05:09,100
with a graceful figure

66
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,180
and a beautiful face,

67
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:15,610
puts himself into

68
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:19,210
the roles that he plays.

69
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:23,070
What a talented performer.

70
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:26,200
I’m shy of the compliment.

71
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:27,780
You are shy already?

72
00:05:28,650 --> 00:05:29,710
Then cover your ears.

73
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,330
The rest words are more exaggerating.

74
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,560
Listen.

75
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:36,510
Shang Xirui’s voice and performance

76
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:37,940
are special in this world.

77
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:41,880
The spirits of the opera

78
00:05:42,659 --> 00:05:43,470
are only

79
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,830
on this actor.

80
00:05:49,130 --> 00:05:49,900
Me?

81
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,710
You.

82
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:52,220
OK.

83
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:54,980
Xiao Lai. Give Mr. Du award.

84
00:05:55,550 --> 00:05:58,640
OK. He should be handsomely rewarded.

85
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,460
Look, you’ve gained weight,

86
00:06:03,590 --> 00:06:06,060
but he still says that you have a graceful figure.

87
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,110
Have I gained weight?

88
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,250
Of course.

89
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:10,600
Look at this robe.

90
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:13,690
It was still loose on the Mid-autumn Festival.

91
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:16,020
But now, it’s almost burst.

92
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,340
You had

93
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:21,310
a lot of activities recently.

94
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,990
And after the activities, you had feasts.

95
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:26,020
Mr. Cheng called you

96
00:06:26,450 --> 00:06:28,950
to have night snacks every day.

97
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:30,640
No wonder that you’ve put on weight.

98
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:31,800
You reminded me.

99
00:06:31,810 --> 00:06:34,159
The tofu that I ate yesterday was really delicious.

100
00:06:34,210 --> 00:06:35,940
I can still feel the cream.

101
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:37,570
You can stop.

102
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:40,260
I’m afraid that you can’t

103
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:42,159
even bow when worshipping the pioneer,

104
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:45,340
not to mention back bending.

105
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:46,940
Let me show you now.

106
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:47,590
Look carefully.

107
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,500
Alright. Alright.

108
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:50,140
You can stop

109
00:06:50,150 --> 00:06:52,080
in case the robe becomes dirty again.

110
00:06:53,690 --> 00:06:55,200
Is it hard to lose weight?

111
00:06:55,710 --> 00:06:58,340
After playing martial arts plots for half a month,

112
00:06:58,350 --> 00:06:59,960
I can become as thin as a monkey.

113
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:03,470
Layue, is the incense table ready?

114
00:07:03,910 --> 00:07:04,870
Layue!

115
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,280
Stop calling him.

116
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,670
I asked him to buy fruits for the worship.

117
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:16,150
Where is Fengtai. Hasn’t he woken up?

118
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,360
He went out in the morning.

119
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:45,000
Have you known it?

120
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,240
I said it.

121
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,740
My brother invested in a troupe

122
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,400
without telling you.

123
00:07:57,620 --> 00:07:58,990
This is what a playboy does.

124
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:00,640
It’s shameless.

125
00:08:02,570 --> 00:08:05,780
I just settled the problem

126
00:08:05,790 --> 00:08:07,000
with Cao Guixiu

127
00:08:07,150 --> 00:08:08,770
and was going to tell you this.

128
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:10,420
Will you tell me?

129
00:08:11,030 --> 00:08:12,220
He’s your brother.

130
00:08:12,230 --> 00:08:14,200
Of course you’ll help him.

131
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:16,440
Look at you.

132
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:18,260
I swear I said the truth.

133
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:20,390
Every time you had a quarrel,

134
00:08:20,910 --> 00:08:22,720
I always helped you.

135
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:28,250
OK, so how will you help me

136
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:29,320
this time?

137
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,960
If you like,

138
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,080
I’ll shout and hit him.

139
00:08:34,350 --> 00:08:35,720
If these are not enough,

140
00:08:35,850 --> 00:08:37,970
I’ll drive him out.

141
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,169
OK, I have your words.

142
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,460
Is this a big deal?

143
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:49,650
Call Chacha’er to have breakfast.

144
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:51,710
She needs to learn the discipline.

145
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:54,600
I saw her going to the back garden.

146
00:08:58,900 --> 00:08:59,470
This is for you.

147
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:01,010
What’s this?

148
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,630
Bill for the meal. Take it.

149
00:09:03,470 --> 00:09:05,210
The meal is free.

150
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,250
Take it.

151
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:19,920
It’s a gift to thank you.

152
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,440
No, I can’t take it.

153
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:24,920
I don’t accept gifts casually.

154
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:27,760
When you gave me money,

155
00:09:27,770 --> 00:09:29,110
I accepted it without hesitation.

156
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:30,720
You liked to accept mine.

157
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,480
But I don’t like to accept yours.

158
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:34,720
It doesn’t make sense. Just take it.

159
00:09:35,290 --> 00:09:36,390
My sister-in-law told me

160
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,960
that we never owe others.

161
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:42,590
I can’t accept your gift.

162
00:09:43,070 --> 00:09:44,170
Our leader also said

163
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,860
that people in our troupe

164
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:46,750
are all upright.

165
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,020
We never owe others as well.

166
00:09:48,490 --> 00:09:49,130
You must take it.

167
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,600
I... I can’t.

168
00:09:50,610 --> 00:09:51,660
Take it.

169
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:53,460
-I can’t. Take it back.
-Don’t refuse.

170
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:54,100
Take it.

171
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:55,080
Take it.

172
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:55,860
I can’t.

173
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:56,820
I beg you. This is a gift for you.

174
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:57,940
What are you doing?

175
00:09:57,950 --> 00:09:58,660
Hold it.

176
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,800
-Chacha’er!
-Take it.

177
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:05,960
I was scared to death.

178
00:10:08,350 --> 00:10:09,220
Fengtai.

179
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,920
Fengtai. Did you hear it?

180
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,600
Yes.

181
00:10:15,430 --> 00:10:16,900
Your sister just watched an opera

182
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,230
at Shuiyun Theater.

183
00:10:18,470 --> 00:10:20,020
It’s not a big deal.

184
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:23,220
She also knows

185
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,380
that we invested in the theater.

186
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:25,890
That’s fine.

187
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:28,270
I won’t bother to tell her.

188
00:10:31,010 --> 00:10:33,860
Your sister didn’t quarrel with me last night,

189
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:35,700
which means it’s not hopeless at all.

190
00:10:37,130 --> 00:10:37,880
Really?

191
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:38,910
Yes.

192
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,580
Fine.

193
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:44,960
I can be relived.

194
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,760
Made in America?

195
00:10:55,410 --> 00:10:56,630
It’s a gift for Mr. Shang.

196
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:57,970
Let me have a taste.

197
00:10:57,980 --> 00:10:59,400
I’ll buy him a new one.

198
00:11:01,290 --> 00:11:02,960
How come you grab goodies from a child?

199
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:04,320
Greedy-guts.

200
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:06,480
Who’s a child?

201
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:08,980
He’s a man in twenties.

202
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:10,160
A child?

203
00:11:10,350 --> 00:11:12,260
He’s innocent and friendly.

204
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:14,060
And he’s always frank.

205
00:11:14,070 --> 00:11:15,310
Only a child behaves like that.

206
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:17,510
Pioneer,

207
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:21,650
I, Shang Xirui, worship you every year

208
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:24,900
with all kinds of food.

209
00:11:25,510 --> 00:11:27,550
I never missed this ceremony.

210
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,480
I worship you with all my heart.

211
00:11:31,130 --> 00:11:34,660
With your protection, we lived well

212
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:36,000
in Pingyang.

213
00:11:36,430 --> 00:11:39,840
And now, our Shuiyun Theater also

214
00:11:39,850 --> 00:11:41,280
needs your protection

215
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:44,370
to earn money for Mr. Cheng.

216
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,440
When the money is enough,

217
00:11:46,770 --> 00:11:49,830
I’ll offer you a gold body and religious rites.

218
00:11:49,990 --> 00:11:52,540
Won’t you introduce Mr. Cheng?

219
00:11:53,260 --> 00:11:56,280
Otherwise the pioneer doesn’t know him.

220
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:58,560
Our pioneer is an immortal.

221
00:11:59,170 --> 00:12:01,820
He knows everything

222
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:03,540
though we don’t tell him.

223
00:12:03,890 --> 00:12:05,420
He must know

224
00:12:05,430 --> 00:12:07,630
who you are.

225
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,280
Of course.

226
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,920
I was God of Wisdom in my last life.

227
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:13,800
When I was in heaven,

228
00:12:14,410 --> 00:12:17,840
I worked with him in the palace.

229
00:12:18,050 --> 00:12:19,990
Mr. Du, stop bragging.

230
00:12:20,070 --> 00:12:22,460
Were you a colleague of our pioneer?

231
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:26,390
The worship hasn’t been finished! Be serious!

232
00:12:27,190 --> 00:12:28,810
Behave yourselves in front of the pioneer.

233
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:34,050
Excuse me,

234
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:37,030
is Shang Xirui living here?

235
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:04,270
Mr. Shang. It’s here.

236
00:13:06,890 --> 00:13:08,980
Mrs. Cheng. Mr. Shang is here.

237
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,560
Mr. Shang.

238
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,590
Good morning, Mrs. Cheng.

239
00:13:35,850 --> 00:13:39,270
Thanks for remembering me.

240
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,900
You left before I finished the opera

241
00:13:42,370 --> 00:13:44,090
War in Wan City that day.

242
00:13:44,330 --> 00:13:46,360
So I didn’t thank you personally.

243
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:48,780
When we play another good opera,

244
00:13:49,050 --> 00:13:50,530
I’ll ask my staff to give you a ticket.

245
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:52,900
What a good opera?

246
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:55,820
Will you really perform Ms. Wang?

247
00:13:58,780 --> 00:14:00,450
I didn’t play that old woman.

248
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:02,540
I’m afraid that I can’t do it well.

249
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,010
But if you like,

250
00:14:05,310 --> 00:14:06,530
I’ll perform that specially for you

251
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:08,010
when we have a rest.

252
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:10,430
Don’t pretend to be innocent.

253
00:14:11,070 --> 00:14:11,820
Tell me.

254
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:15,010
Is there a performer named La Yuehong

255
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,960
in your theater?

256
00:14:18,070 --> 00:14:19,290
Yes, there is.

257
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:20,310
Go.

258
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:31,800
Mrs. Cheng, this...

259
00:14:33,190 --> 00:14:37,230
It is said that your Shuiyun Theater is full of elites,

260
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:39,430
but I think it’s full of thieves.

261
00:14:39,930 --> 00:14:42,670
Look, he’s the typical one.

262
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:45,820
He went to our back garden secretly in the morning,

263
00:14:46,070 --> 00:14:48,060
and molested Miss Cheng.

264
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:50,520
Did he try to steal things

265
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:52,040
or the lady?

266
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:54,380
I would call the police

267
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:55,960
and sue him for trespassing

268
00:14:56,010 --> 00:14:58,400
if not given that he’s too young.

269
00:14:58,990 --> 00:15:00,660
Leader, I didn’t steal anything.

270
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:01,730
Why did you go to Cheng Mansion?

271
00:15:02,430 --> 00:15:02,890
Last time...

272
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:05,180
Mr. Shang. Question him carefully

273
00:15:05,190 --> 00:15:06,380
after you’re back.

274
00:15:07,110 --> 00:15:09,060
I’m even shamed

275
00:15:09,070 --> 00:15:11,000
to hear the filthy things.

276
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,720
Mrs. Cheng, I need to make this clear

277
00:15:13,730 --> 00:15:15,540
in front of the two parties.

278
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,740
Do you need to?

279
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:19,240
What else would a performer do

280
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,860
in my mansion without invitation?

281
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:21,420
This is slander!

282
00:15:21,430 --> 00:15:21,990
Shut up!

283
00:15:27,090 --> 00:15:27,890
Mrs. Cheng.

284
00:15:29,310 --> 00:15:32,740
Why are performers labeled filthy people?

285
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:34,430
Look.

286
00:15:34,950 --> 00:15:36,580
He’s so hot-tempered.

287
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,520
No wonder that my cousin-in-law

288
00:15:39,530 --> 00:15:41,740
was bullied terribly in Pingyang.

289
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:47,460
Think about the most popular performers in Peking.

290
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:50,540
To buy opium,

291
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:52,920
Hou Yukui sold his assets and children.

292
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,160
He made his daughter who was 18

293
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:56,160
marry an old man aged 68.

294
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:58,560
What a ruthless man.

295
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,380
And Ning Jiulang

296
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:03,270
was born to be a slave.

297
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:06,160
After being driven out of the Palace,

298
00:16:06,170 --> 00:16:09,240
he served in Qi Mansion.

299
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:10,750
And your dad...

300
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:14,180
What’s the name of your dad?

301
00:16:14,190 --> 00:16:16,300
Mrs. Cheng, his name is Shang Juzhen.

302
00:16:16,340 --> 00:16:18,300
He worked in a freight agent before.

303
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:20,420
He also went to our entertainment party once.

304
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,990
Shang Juzhen.

305
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,070
He kowtowed

306
00:16:26,730 --> 00:16:28,140
even before performing.

307
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:31,210
He took a maid as a lady.

308
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:33,450
That maid was so embarrassed of it.

309
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:42,610
The popular performers

310
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:44,560
are all snobbish.

311
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,280
Fish begins to stink at the head.

312
00:16:46,290 --> 00:16:48,580
So the young performers won’t be good.

313
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:50,080
They may commit something worse than stealing,

314
00:16:50,090 --> 00:16:52,250
like murder or arson.

315
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:56,310
Take your little thief back.

316
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:58,570
Please go back, Mr. Shang.

317
00:17:01,290 --> 00:17:02,600
Mrs. Cheng, your story is wrong.

318
00:17:03,770 --> 00:17:05,720
Hou Yukui used opium

319
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,210
to relieve his pain,

320
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:08,650
not for pleasure.

321
00:17:09,730 --> 00:17:12,520
Ning Jiulang served the royal family

322
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:15,130
and he was grateful to his master.

323
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:17,180
Why is he snobbish in your words?

324
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:40,420
Mr. Chen. Mr. Chen.

325
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:41,530
Look here, Mr. Chen.

326
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:44,250
Mr. Chen. Mr. Chen.

327
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:45,620
I like you!

328
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:51,350
Mr. Chen. Mr. Chen.

329
00:17:51,630 --> 00:17:52,860
Please be quiet.

330
00:17:52,870 --> 00:17:53,670
Be quiet.

331
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:56,960
Journalists ask questions first.

332
00:17:57,050 --> 00:17:58,660
Then, you can take photos with Mr. Chen.

333
00:17:58,670 --> 00:17:59,250
OK?

334
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:01,300
Mr. Chen gained appreciation of the emperor.

335
00:18:01,310 --> 00:18:02,800
We are proud of you.

336
00:18:02,810 --> 00:18:03,620
Besides the emperor,

337
00:18:03,630 --> 00:18:04,930
the foreigners like your opera very much.

338
00:18:04,940 --> 00:18:06,580
Mr. Chen, very good.

339
00:18:06,700 --> 00:18:07,500
I’m flattered.

340
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:08,100
It’s time for photos.

341
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:09,440
Mr. Chen. Look here.

342
00:18:12,340 --> 00:18:13,270
Mr. Chen. Look here.

343
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:15,900
Alright. We need to finish.

344
00:18:16,390 --> 00:18:16,980
Come on.

345
00:18:18,010 --> 00:18:19,650
OK. OK. Please leave there.

346
00:18:20,230 --> 00:18:21,050
We need to finish.

347
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:22,380
And me.

348
00:18:22,390 --> 00:18:23,010
Thanks.

349
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:23,950
Look here.

350
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:25,570
The left.

351
00:18:26,770 --> 00:18:27,230
OK.

352
00:18:27,350 --> 00:18:28,140
Mr. Chen.

353
00:18:28,980 --> 00:18:29,580
Mr. Chen.

354
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,330
Thanks.

355
00:18:30,850 --> 00:18:31,430
Look here.

356
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:32,630
Here, please.

357
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:36,200
Excuse me.

358
00:18:36,210 --> 00:18:36,820
Thank you all.

359
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:38,620
Can I talk with Renxiang alone?

360
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:39,860
Come.

361
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:41,430
Mr. Chen.

362
00:18:41,740 --> 00:18:42,640
Mr. Chen.

363
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:44,580
Don’t go. Mr. Chen.

364
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:45,140
Don’t go.

365
00:18:45,150 --> 00:18:45,820
Mr. Chen.

366
00:18:45,830 --> 00:18:46,920
Mr. Chen. Mr. Chen.

367
00:18:46,930 --> 00:18:47,480
Sorry.

368
00:18:47,490 --> 00:18:48,980
Did you hear what I said?

369
00:18:49,190 --> 00:18:50,520
-Yes. Yes.
-Mr. Chen has something now.

370
00:18:50,530 --> 00:18:53,090
I received 8 telegrams from you during 3 days.

371
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,520
I almost didn’t sleep

372
00:18:54,530 --> 00:18:55,860
during the journey.

373
00:18:55,930 --> 00:18:57,590
Don’t I need to take a breath?

374
00:18:58,190 --> 00:18:59,340
They are my hard-die fans

375
00:18:59,350 --> 00:19:00,900
from everywhere of our country.

376
00:19:00,910 --> 00:19:02,320
I have no reason to leave now.

377
00:19:02,330 --> 00:19:03,020
Wait me for a while.

378
00:19:03,190 --> 00:19:03,610
Just wait.

379
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:05,000
I’ll be back later.

380
00:19:05,330 --> 00:19:06,940
Come back.

381
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:10,670
How dare you ignore me after being popular?

382
00:19:11,190 --> 00:19:12,220
Gosh.

383
00:19:12,710 --> 00:19:13,780
When you were young,

384
00:19:14,650 --> 00:19:16,540
-if my family...
-If your family

385
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:17,980
hadn’t helped my mother and me,

386
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,190
we would end up dying from hunger

387
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:20,430
without being noticed.

388
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:23,220
I really appreciate it.

389
00:19:23,230 --> 00:19:24,500
Let me kowtow to you.

390
00:19:24,510 --> 00:19:25,780
No, no. Renxiang.

391
00:19:28,090 --> 00:19:29,440
What are you doing?

392
00:19:30,090 --> 00:19:31,640
OK, I know.

393
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:32,890
You don’t want to go back with me?

394
00:19:34,340 --> 00:19:36,300
I’ll tell my aunt.

395
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:39,680
Adults don’t report anything to parents.

396
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:41,390
OK. I go back with you.

397
00:19:41,470 --> 00:19:43,100
I’ll go back. Just wait a moment.

398
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:45,430
I’m sorry, everyone.

399
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:49,000
I have something important to do. See you.

400
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:49,730
Mr. Chen!

401
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:50,310
Sorry.

402
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,530
Mr. Chen! Don’t go!

403
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:53,700
Put my things at home

404
00:19:53,710 --> 00:19:54,820
and tell my mother

405
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:55,900
that I’ll eat at my uncle’s place.

406
00:19:55,910 --> 00:19:56,680
OK.

407
00:19:57,110 --> 00:20:01,580
Mr. Chen! Mr. Chen! Mr. Chen!

408
00:20:02,690 --> 00:20:04,880
Take care! Take care!

409
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:16,680
Xirui, this is too violent to me.

410
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:18,460
Leader.

411
00:20:18,890 --> 00:20:20,980
Leader. The punishment is enough.

412
00:20:21,110 --> 00:20:22,640
La Yuehong’s realized his mistake.

413
00:20:22,650 --> 00:20:23,910
You can stop, leader.

414
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:26,990
Why did you go to Cheng Mansion

415
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:27,940
and do filthy things!

416
00:20:27,950 --> 00:20:29,470
I didn’t do filthy things.

417
00:20:29,810 --> 00:20:31,020
I did nothing wrong.

418
00:20:31,430 --> 00:20:32,410
I just talked

419
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:34,070
with Miss Cheng.

420
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,750
You talked with her at the back garden?

421
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:38,000
Shame on you!

422
00:20:38,140 --> 00:20:39,890
What did you talk with Miss Cheng?

423
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,320
You can talk with Mr. Cheng,

424
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:43,060
so why can’t I talk with Miss Cheng?

425
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:43,770
You won’t get away with it!

426
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:46,080
Yuehong. Don’t you want him to stop?

427
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,460
-Leader.
-Leader.

428
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:50,650
What happened?

429
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:52,360
Mr. Cheng. Mr. Cheng.

430
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:54,770
When I entered your lane,

431
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:57,690
I heard the cry and the shout.

432
00:20:57,760 --> 00:20:59,070
It’s good that you are here.

433
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:01,120
Hurry.

434
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:03,820
Stubborn boy. Take him back to his room.

435
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:04,920
Hurry. Hurry.

436
00:21:04,930 --> 00:21:05,640
Hurry up.

437
00:21:06,070 --> 00:21:06,890
Hurry.

438
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:08,580
Take care.

439
00:21:09,380 --> 00:21:10,260
Take care.

440
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:11,440
Go.

441
00:21:12,830 --> 00:21:13,620
How stubborn he is.

442
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:14,710
Hurry. Hurry.

443
00:21:34,370 --> 00:21:35,330
What are you doing?

444
00:21:35,340 --> 00:21:37,700
Mr. Cheng, I’ll hand over our profits

445
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:39,300
every month.

446
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:42,290
Just wait for it at home.

447
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:46,090
Please don’t come to our filthy place anymore

448
00:21:46,290 --> 00:21:49,030
in case I offend Mrs. Wealth.

449
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:50,450
Mr. Shang!

450
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:52,780
Mr. Cheng. Mr. Shang said it clearly.

451
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:54,170
Please go back now.

452
00:21:54,180 --> 00:21:55,050
Xiao Lai.

453
00:21:55,230 --> 00:21:56,770
What on earth happened?

454
00:21:58,660 --> 00:21:59,850
I’ll return this as well.

455
00:21:59,930 --> 00:22:02,100
Ask your

456
00:22:02,110 --> 00:22:04,010
eloquent Mrs. Cheng about it.

457
00:22:08,990 --> 00:22:10,470
This opera performer?

458
00:22:11,220 --> 00:22:13,020
I gave him American cookies,

459
00:22:13,570 --> 00:22:15,350
but he gave me a cold-shoulder.

460
00:22:21,540 --> 00:22:22,070
Dad.

461
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:27,560
Uncle. Sorry that I’m late.

462
00:22:27,570 --> 00:22:28,560
Wish you well.

463
00:22:30,650 --> 00:22:32,210
It’s good that you are safe and sound.

464
00:22:32,220 --> 00:22:33,380
Stand up. The floor is cold.

465
00:22:33,390 --> 00:22:34,460
Hurry up.

466
00:22:34,470 --> 00:22:35,020
Stand up.

467
00:22:36,820 --> 00:22:38,570
I didn’t let you kneel

468
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:40,680
even when you played Susan in your childhood.

469
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:43,160
Come to have lunch.

470
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:44,730
My dad is always good to you.

471
00:22:45,620 --> 00:22:47,090
Only three of us.

472
00:22:48,430 --> 00:22:50,200
These are all your favorite.

473
00:23:01,460 --> 00:23:03,030
When you left,

474
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:05,220
the door was with a bamboo curtain,

475
00:23:05,870 --> 00:23:07,800
through which we could see the pomegranate.

476
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:11,110
And now, we’ve hung the cotton curtain.

477
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,860
The old people always feel that

478
00:23:15,870 --> 00:23:17,600
time flies by.

479
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:22,100
One day I’ll leave

480
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:23,520
you two and

481
00:23:24,150 --> 00:23:26,020
this troupe ever.

482
00:23:27,530 --> 00:23:29,720
This is what I worry about.

483
00:23:30,410 --> 00:23:32,710
Uncle, don’t say that.

484
00:23:33,730 --> 00:23:35,070
You are still spirited.

485
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:37,020
Seems that you are stronger than me.

486
00:23:38,490 --> 00:23:39,530
No.

487
00:23:40,730 --> 00:23:41,810
I’m old.

488
00:23:43,150 --> 00:23:45,300
For the one year that you left,

489
00:23:46,130 --> 00:23:49,460
even a young boy dares to offend me.

490
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,190
Who?

491
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,810
You are the chairman of the Opera Association.

492
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:57,380
Does anyone dare to be against you?

493
00:23:57,390 --> 00:23:58,230
Yes.

494
00:23:59,430 --> 00:24:00,900
Shang Xirui.

495
00:24:01,530 --> 00:24:03,820
He was popular even when you were here.

496
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,600
After you left,

497
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:07,290
he’s drawn all the attention.

498
00:24:07,300 --> 00:24:09,500
He plays operas back-to-back.

499
00:24:09,530 --> 00:24:11,480
Other performers even don’t have a stage.

500
00:24:12,630 --> 00:24:14,380
Look at the newspaper.

501
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:19,590
Shang Xirui intends to be the king of opera.

502
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:21,610
Look. How arrogant he is!

503
00:24:25,950 --> 00:24:28,000
I called you back

504
00:24:28,910 --> 00:24:30,440
because of him.

505
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:36,100
Cheng Fengtai

506
00:24:36,450 --> 00:24:39,080
started his business again with his wife’s dowry.

507
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:40,920
Of course he’s henpecked.

508
00:24:41,010 --> 00:24:41,990
Wait and see.

509
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,650
If he

510
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:45,020
argues with his wife,

511
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:48,260
your theater will go up in smoke.

512
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:50,650
I’m serious.

513
00:24:51,650 --> 00:24:53,640
Mr. Cheng is not reliable.

514
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:56,460
What you’ll rely on is still me.

515
00:24:57,870 --> 00:24:59,110
Mr. Du.

516
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:02,020
Can you persuade Commander Cao

517
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:03,850
or buy us a theater?

518
00:25:04,460 --> 00:25:06,360
After writing a new play,

519
00:25:06,370 --> 00:25:08,470
you were almost driven out by Du Hanlin.

520
00:25:09,550 --> 00:25:11,490
Maybe one day

521
00:25:11,500 --> 00:25:12,700
you’ll sleep

522
00:25:12,710 --> 00:25:14,250
in our Shuiyun Theater.

523
00:25:14,710 --> 00:25:15,940
Yes.

524
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:16,980
Shijiu.

525
00:25:17,110 --> 00:25:19,660
You really need to prepare a room for me.

526
00:25:20,410 --> 00:25:21,440
OK. OK.

527
00:25:21,450 --> 00:25:23,380
It’s not time to argue.

528
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,740
Leader. You refused

529
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:26,800
Mr. Cheng to go in Shuiyun Theater.

530
00:25:26,910 --> 00:25:28,400
It’s fine if

531
00:25:28,410 --> 00:25:29,670
you don’t feel guilty.

532
00:25:29,980 --> 00:25:30,980
His wife scolded me,

533
00:25:30,990 --> 00:25:32,020
so why should I feel guilty?

534
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:33,250
-Mr. Cheng...
-Leader...
-Stop!

535
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,400
He’s our God of Wealth.

536
00:25:34,410 --> 00:25:36,490
Those who come from wealthy families

537
00:25:36,670 --> 00:25:38,400
always look down on us.

538
00:25:38,710 --> 00:25:40,300
He made rules once he took over Shuiyun.

539
00:25:40,650 --> 00:25:42,180
Also, he let us sign the contract.

540
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:44,260
Now, everything has been finished,

541
00:25:44,460 --> 00:25:46,140
but he’s gone.

542
00:25:46,150 --> 00:25:47,360
-Yes, leader.
-Leader.

543
00:25:47,370 --> 00:25:49,270
-How about our contract?
-He’s gone.

544
00:25:50,260 --> 00:25:51,890
This is what I’ll say.

545
00:25:52,460 --> 00:25:54,850
Leader, will you still use the regulation

546
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:55,980
made by him?

547
00:25:55,990 --> 00:25:56,720
Yes.

548
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,730
What’s the regulation?

549
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:04,370
These new rules.

550
00:26:04,430 --> 00:26:05,220
Have you forgotten?

551
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:06,620
First,

552
00:26:06,780 --> 00:26:09,290
no one can use the money of our theater.

553
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:11,130
What? This is weird.

554
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:12,310
What if we get diseases?

555
00:26:12,320 --> 00:26:14,990
-What should we do?
-This is good.

556
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:16,860
Do you understand?

557
00:26:17,620 --> 00:26:19,030
You have no room for greediness.

558
00:26:19,290 --> 00:26:19,960
Next.

559
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:23,080
Second, the performers

560
00:26:23,090 --> 00:26:24,330
will get 8 dollars every month.

561
00:26:24,630 --> 00:26:26,620
-And the surplus is the Performance.
-Only 8 dollars?

562
00:26:26,970 --> 00:26:28,020
Performance?

563
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:30,130
What does it mean?

564
00:26:30,390 --> 00:26:31,620
Who knows

565
00:26:31,630 --> 00:26:33,070
the terms of business?

566
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:34,820
This means

567
00:26:34,830 --> 00:26:37,580
that everyone will get the same payment,

568
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:38,420
which is 8 dollars.

569
00:26:38,430 --> 00:26:39,770
Really?

570
00:26:39,850 --> 00:26:40,890
It’s even less than the half of our previous salary.

571
00:26:40,900 --> 00:26:42,580
That’s not enough to buy alcohol.

572
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,760
Stop complaining!

573
00:26:43,910 --> 00:26:45,480
I’ll give you bonus at the end of the year.

574
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:47,570
-Do we have bonus?
-It’s nice.

575
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:48,570
-Bonus?
-Bonus?

576
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,320
Next!

577
00:26:50,970 --> 00:26:51,940
Next,

578
00:26:52,650 --> 00:26:54,600
young or old,

579
00:26:54,820 --> 00:26:56,240
everyone has a chance to step on the stage.

580
00:26:56,250 --> 00:26:56,660
Really?

581
00:26:56,670 --> 00:26:57,960
-We’ll step on the stage?
-Make an arrangement.

582
00:26:58,610 --> 00:26:59,890
Why?

583
00:26:59,970 --> 00:27:01,070
Dream on.

584
00:27:01,210 --> 00:27:02,670
How can you step on the stage?

585
00:27:02,810 --> 00:27:04,010
Are you qualified?

586
00:27:04,020 --> 00:27:05,100
In your dreams.

587
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:06,160
Yes.

588
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,420
How can you perform?

589
00:27:07,430 --> 00:27:09,100
I don’t need to explain it.

590
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:12,450
The freshmen who studies opera well

591
00:27:12,890 --> 00:27:15,180
will have a chance to show themselves.

592
00:27:15,910 --> 00:27:17,380
It’s deal.

593
00:27:18,020 --> 00:27:18,750
Go back.

594
00:27:18,950 --> 00:27:20,680
I’ll discuss the new play with Mr. Du.

595
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:21,410
Don’t bother us.

596
00:27:21,790 --> 00:27:22,340
But, leader...

597
00:27:22,350 --> 00:27:23,510
-Think it over.
-Thanks, leader.

598
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:24,270
Thanks, leader.

599
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:25,120
OK. Go back.

600
00:27:25,130 --> 00:27:26,570
It’s really 8 dollars, leader?

601
00:27:27,060 --> 00:27:27,780
Stage, I’m coming!

602
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:28,250
Yes.

603
00:27:28,260 --> 00:27:30,250
How can you do it well?

604
00:27:38,910 --> 00:27:40,270
You’ve almost finished it.

605
00:27:43,010 --> 00:27:45,980
Come on. I don’t like to eat.

606
00:27:45,990 --> 00:27:47,070
Too sweet.

607
00:27:51,330 --> 00:27:52,920
We all know that

608
00:27:53,170 --> 00:27:54,840
Shang Xirui is annoying.

609
00:27:55,010 --> 00:27:57,830
But his biggest problem is adapting operas.

610
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:02,190
I watched Hero Li Jun adapted by him.

611
00:28:02,460 --> 00:28:03,720
It’s quite fresh.

612
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:05,260
I don’t think it’s a problem.

613
00:28:06,150 --> 00:28:07,300
Of course it’s a problem.

614
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,870
You don’t know that

615
00:28:10,150 --> 00:28:12,280
it becomes further intensified during the one year.

616
00:28:12,710 --> 00:28:14,110
Adapt opera randomly.

617
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:16,250
He shows no respect to the tradition.

618
00:28:17,430 --> 00:28:19,510
My dad coughed after seeing that.

619
00:28:20,790 --> 00:28:21,900
It is rude.

620
00:28:27,540 --> 00:28:29,660
He can’t do it randomly.

621
00:28:30,190 --> 00:28:32,180
The classic operas

622
00:28:32,190 --> 00:28:33,520
are like Bibles.

623
00:28:33,710 --> 00:28:34,930
Is Shang Xirui

624
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:36,360
wiser than our ancestors?

625
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:40,120
So,

626
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:42,210
I was called back

627
00:28:43,510 --> 00:28:44,300
to stop Shang Xirui

628
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:45,900
adapting operas?

629
00:28:48,250 --> 00:28:50,980
Uncle, you are a senior.

630
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:52,500
He doesn’t even listen to you.

631
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:53,830
How can I stop him?

632
00:28:53,910 --> 00:28:54,620
Also,

633
00:28:54,630 --> 00:28:56,260
Shang Xirui has a bad temper.

634
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:57,660
He may hurt me.

635
00:28:58,430 --> 00:28:59,520
I won’t get myself involved.

636
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,510
Look how coward you are.

637
00:29:03,300 --> 00:29:06,390
He’ll be punished by audiences for it.

638
00:29:06,810 --> 00:29:09,050
We don’t need to bother.

639
00:29:11,430 --> 00:29:13,360
I asked you back

640
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:16,340
because I want you

641
00:29:17,350 --> 00:29:18,760
to compete against him.

642
00:29:22,390 --> 00:29:24,040
Do you dare?

643
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:29,200
Do you understand?

644
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,000
How about I read it for you?

645
00:29:32,990 --> 00:29:34,930
No need. I’ve remembered.

646
00:29:35,230 --> 00:29:36,380
I can even recite what you shouted

647
00:29:36,390 --> 00:29:38,120
to me when you entered.

648
00:29:39,430 --> 00:29:40,960
Stop showing off.

649
00:29:41,470 --> 00:29:43,590
I know you have a good memory.

650
00:29:43,910 --> 00:29:44,560
I trust you.

651
00:29:45,470 --> 00:29:46,280
Tell me.

652
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:48,360
Which play do you like?

653
00:29:51,870 --> 00:29:53,640
You like none of the three?

654
00:29:54,190 --> 00:29:55,600
Your stories

655
00:29:56,050 --> 00:29:57,790
are almost the same.

656
00:29:58,870 --> 00:30:01,920
They are all about loyalty,

657
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:04,500
steadfastness,

658
00:30:04,830 --> 00:30:06,430
filial piety,

659
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:08,480
or family.

660
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:10,750
We can find the shadow of other plays.

661
00:30:10,870 --> 00:30:13,260
Not interesting.

662
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:15,810
You are so picky.

663
00:30:15,990 --> 00:30:16,800
Tell me

664
00:30:17,380 --> 00:30:19,220
what kind of story is interesting?

665
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:22,460
I want a role

666
00:30:22,470 --> 00:30:23,970
never shown in opera.

667
00:30:25,710 --> 00:30:27,910
I also want to create such a role,

668
00:30:28,230 --> 00:30:30,460
but the audiences may not like it.

669
00:30:30,610 --> 00:30:32,640
Why the popular plays are popular?

670
00:30:33,030 --> 00:30:35,150
Because most people like it.

671
00:30:35,290 --> 00:30:37,320
Also, they’ve watched them for many years.

672
00:30:37,430 --> 00:30:39,360
Audiences are used to

673
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,590
the old stories.

674
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:42,180
If we create

675
00:30:42,190 --> 00:30:43,500
a new role,

676
00:30:43,510 --> 00:30:44,200
will it be

677
00:30:45,070 --> 00:30:45,920
well received?

678
00:30:46,290 --> 00:30:48,040
The republic took place of Qing Dynasty.

679
00:30:48,050 --> 00:30:49,520
The president took place of the emperor.

680
00:30:49,530 --> 00:30:51,900
People’s hair style and clothes are all changed.

681
00:30:51,930 --> 00:30:53,580
Why can’t we change the roles

682
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:54,680
in opera?

683
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:56,520
What’s more, all plays are created by artists.

684
00:30:57,250 --> 00:30:58,540
Our ancestors could make good plays.

685
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,730
Why can’t we?

686
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:00,440
Also,

687
00:31:00,450 --> 00:31:02,380
you are my star of wisdom.

688
00:31:02,390 --> 00:31:03,640
I will make it!

689
00:31:03,950 --> 00:31:05,220
Nice!

690
00:31:05,410 --> 00:31:06,860
I’m really touched.

691
00:31:09,630 --> 00:31:10,800
Let me show you something good.

692
00:31:14,180 --> 00:31:14,800
Look at it.

693
00:31:16,870 --> 00:31:18,640
I wrote this

694
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:19,440
when we just met.

695
00:31:19,670 --> 00:31:21,270
For three years,

696
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:23,360
I modified it many times.

697
00:31:23,980 --> 00:31:25,600
Keep a secret from me?

698
00:31:26,910 --> 00:31:28,930
Zhao... Zhao Fei...

699
00:31:28,940 --> 00:31:29,930
Zhao Feiyan.

700
00:31:30,110 --> 00:31:31,220
Yan for Yangtze.

701
00:31:31,230 --> 00:31:32,900
Yes, she’s a maid in the palace at first.

702
00:31:32,910 --> 00:31:34,580
But finally she becomes the queen.

703
00:31:34,970 --> 00:31:35,770
I tell you.

704
00:31:35,780 --> 00:31:37,150
The emperor was charmed by her.

705
00:31:37,390 --> 00:31:38,630
For her, he doesn’t have offspring

706
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:39,840
and also loses his life.

707
00:31:41,510 --> 00:31:42,440
Is it dramatic?

708
00:31:42,450 --> 00:31:44,850
Of course. It’s her.

709
00:31:45,950 --> 00:31:46,970
But the point

710
00:31:47,470 --> 00:31:48,480
is that

711
00:31:48,830 --> 00:31:50,010
Zhao Feiyan

712
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:54,370
dances on the palm,

713
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:55,960
which is not easy to perform.

714
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:57,550
In this story,

715
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:59,450
Zhao Feiyan

716
00:31:59,460 --> 00:32:01,670
can dance on the palm.

717
00:32:02,330 --> 00:32:03,360
I’m trapped in this plot.

718
00:32:03,410 --> 00:32:05,090
Is dancing hard?

719
00:32:05,390 --> 00:32:08,180
Concubine Yang’s dance

720
00:32:08,190 --> 00:32:09,570
is tricky enough,

721
00:32:09,580 --> 00:32:10,540
but I perform it well.

722
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,880
It’s just dancing on the palm.

723
00:32:11,890 --> 00:32:13,360
But they are different.

724
00:32:13,870 --> 00:32:15,560
The emperor has affection to her

725
00:32:15,570 --> 00:32:17,400
because of her dance.

726
00:32:17,410 --> 00:32:19,520
And this makes the play unique.

727
00:32:19,630 --> 00:32:21,140
Think of an idea.

728
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:24,530
Indeed, it’s hard.

729
00:32:25,990 --> 00:32:27,140
Let me think of it.

730
00:32:28,110 --> 00:32:30,010
Dancing on the palm?

731
00:32:34,320 --> 00:32:35,060
Leader.

732
00:32:35,670 --> 00:32:36,700
Chen Renxiang comes.

733
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:39,030
Isn’t this bastard in the northeast?

734
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,030
He’s already back?

735
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:42,460
What a Greek gift.

736
00:32:42,470 --> 00:32:44,160
Will he borrow money? I need to hide away.

737
00:32:44,170 --> 00:32:45,220
I also need to hide away.

738
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:46,780
This bastard can do anything.

739
00:32:46,790 --> 00:32:47,830
Don’t.

740
00:32:47,960 --> 00:32:49,120
Don’t hide yourselves.

741
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:50,540
He’s at the door

742
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:52,980
and said that he has something serious.

743
00:32:53,290 --> 00:32:54,610
Come and see.

744
00:32:57,950 --> 00:32:59,440
The emperor is not tall.

745
00:32:59,570 --> 00:33:01,030
I can even see the top of his head.

746
00:33:01,410 --> 00:33:02,010
Really?

747
00:33:02,020 --> 00:33:03,990
-He’s thin but hot-tempered.
-Really?

748
00:33:04,030 --> 00:33:05,840
Do you know what he asked me first?

749
00:33:07,490 --> 00:33:09,290
Why didn’t your uncle come?

750
00:33:09,620 --> 00:33:11,640
He performed Sweet Dew Temple well.

751
00:33:12,460 --> 00:33:13,620
Look how triumphant

752
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:14,700
this bastard is.

753
00:33:14,710 --> 00:33:16,490
When my uncle performed that opera,

754
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:18,190
he wasn’t born.

755
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,100
How could he know that my uncle did well?

756
00:33:20,830 --> 00:33:21,420
Right?

757
00:33:21,430 --> 00:33:23,600
Mr. Chen, how are you?

758
00:33:25,370 --> 00:33:26,370
Mr. Shang.

759
00:33:37,950 --> 00:33:39,050
Mr. Shang,

760
00:33:40,470 --> 00:33:42,390
It was fine that you didn’t care your look.

761
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:44,850
But now you are a star

762
00:33:45,150 --> 00:33:47,590
and a bigwig of our opera.

763
00:33:47,870 --> 00:33:49,640
You should pay attention to your appearance.

764
00:33:51,490 --> 00:33:52,920
Look at your hair.

765
00:33:53,630 --> 00:33:55,170
So messy.

766
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:58,010
Could you use some hair lotion?

767
00:33:59,710 --> 00:34:01,730
Don’t touch me. I’ll be angry with you.

768
00:34:01,980 --> 00:34:04,130
What brings you by?

769
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:06,500
I won’t come

770
00:34:06,510 --> 00:34:08,150
without a serious thing.

771
00:34:09,230 --> 00:34:10,860
I don’t even want to see you

772
00:34:11,230 --> 00:34:12,900
in rags.

773
00:34:13,630 --> 00:34:14,510
Your leader

774
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:16,280
is an attraction of your troupe.

775
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:18,020
He needs to dress up.

776
00:34:18,350 --> 00:34:20,400
No one can persuade him.

777
00:34:20,469 --> 00:34:21,380
Mr. Chen.

778
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:25,389
Come to the point.

779
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,520
Mr. Du.

780
00:34:29,949 --> 00:34:31,699
I didn’t notice you due to him.

781
00:34:32,540 --> 00:34:34,270
Stop. Say your thing out.

782
00:34:37,159 --> 00:34:38,330
Mr. Shang,

783
00:34:38,909 --> 00:34:40,510
how did you offend my uncle?

784
00:34:40,989 --> 00:34:43,070
He asked me back from thousands of miles away

785
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:44,699
just to let me compete against you.

786
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:45,620
Really?

787
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:46,600
I agreed with it.

788
00:34:47,270 --> 00:34:48,690
So it depends on your attitude.

789
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:51,840
We perform separately.

790
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:53,540
Why should I compete against you?

791
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:55,370
The audience seats are limited in Peking.

792
00:34:57,240 --> 00:34:58,880
A ticket is quite expensive.

793
00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:02,040
If the audiences watch you this week,

794
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,200
they can’t watch others.

795
00:35:04,090 --> 00:35:06,300
Grabbing others’ job is like killing their parents.

796
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:08,270
Don’t you think this is a reason?

797
00:35:09,850 --> 00:35:11,210
If so,

798
00:35:11,220 --> 00:35:12,580
did our leader kill

799
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:14,300
Jiang Shourong’s parents?

800
00:35:14,570 --> 00:35:16,080
Then he also killed

801
00:35:16,090 --> 00:35:17,600
Jiang Dengbao’s parents?

802
00:35:18,290 --> 00:35:20,450
Jiang Shourong

803
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:21,600
was also killed?

804
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:23,930
What a disaster.

805
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:29,360
I’m right here.

806
00:35:32,890 --> 00:35:34,160
Mr. Shang?

807
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:37,380
Since he asked for a competition, I’ll accept it.

808
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:40,540
I have a new play.

809
00:35:40,930 --> 00:35:42,900
It will be shown on the competition stage.

810
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:45,540
It’s still up in the air.

811
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:46,470
How come you show this play?

812
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:51,620
How to decide on a result?

813
00:35:51,750 --> 00:35:52,400
It’s easy.

814
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,860
We perform

815
00:35:54,930 --> 00:35:56,360
at the same time.

816
00:35:58,150 --> 00:36:01,380
The one who attracts more audiences at the end wins.

817
00:36:01,390 --> 00:36:03,600
It’s not interesting without a wager.

818
00:36:03,830 --> 00:36:06,080
What’s the punishment for the loser?

819
00:36:06,810 --> 00:36:09,570
The loser can’t step on the stage for a year.

820
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:10,910
A year is too long.

821
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,220
That’s fine.

822
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:15,280
I’ll add one more.

823
00:36:16,010 --> 00:36:16,870
Mr. Shang.

824
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:19,740
You’ll lose much.

825
00:36:19,750 --> 00:36:21,180
Are you sure that I’ll lose?

826
00:36:21,190 --> 00:36:22,000
Of course.

827
00:36:23,020 --> 00:36:24,530
What I add is

828
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:28,440
that the loser will shave his hair.

829
00:36:29,090 --> 00:36:30,090
Shave hair?

830
00:36:30,100 --> 00:36:31,210
Shave hair?

831
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:33,590
This is good.

832
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:36,550
We need to add it

833
00:36:36,580 --> 00:36:38,090
because your uncle is Jiang Rongshou.

834
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,100
Do you think so?

835
00:36:39,220 --> 00:36:40,190
Yes.

836
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:47,150
Shave hair! Shave hair!

837
00:36:56,500 --> 00:36:57,780
A good punishment.

838
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:13,720
Xirui.

839
00:37:14,110 --> 00:37:15,210
How naughty you are.

840
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:16,630
He was scared to death.

841
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:18,490
Because he judged my hair.

842
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:19,790
What’s wrong with my hair?

843
00:37:19,950 --> 00:37:21,510
I look better than him after making up.

844
00:37:21,910 --> 00:37:25,390
Leader, I fear we don’t have enough time for the new play.

845
00:37:25,700 --> 00:37:27,580
Yes, leader. We can’t memorize lines quickly.

846
00:37:27,630 --> 00:37:29,220
But I told him so.

847
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:30,560
I never break my words.

848
00:37:30,570 --> 00:37:32,140
This is not my own business.

849
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:34,280
This relates the honor of Shuiyun Theater.

850
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,660
So please work harder.

851
00:37:36,740 --> 00:37:39,380
Leader, how about playing our forte?

852
00:37:39,390 --> 00:37:40,620
It can be a new play after being adapted.

853
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:43,760
I repeat it. We’ll play a new opera.

854
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:45,230
Don’t think about falsification.

855
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:45,960
OK, go back.

856
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:47,340
Leader.

857
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:49,250
Go back.

858
00:37:49,710 --> 00:37:50,450
Chop, chop.

859
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:51,620
-Go.
-But...

860
00:37:54,990 --> 00:37:55,620
Including you.

861
00:38:16,790 --> 00:38:18,260
It’s determined!

862
00:38:19,330 --> 00:38:20,640
We must make it.

863
00:38:21,210 --> 00:38:21,940
As your star of wisdom,

864
00:38:21,950 --> 00:38:23,950
I must work miracles.

865
00:38:24,070 --> 00:38:24,660
It’s settled.

866
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:25,350
Do as what I say.

867
00:38:25,830 --> 00:38:26,840
It has an intermission.

868
00:38:27,110 --> 00:38:28,670
I’ll control it within 40 minutes.

869
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:30,610
The lines and tones are pieces of cake.

870
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:35,020
But that dance...

871
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:36,330
Trust is mutual.

872
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:37,370
Polish your script.

873
00:38:37,380 --> 00:38:38,990
I’ll practice the dance.

874
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:14,540
It looks gorgeous on you.

875
00:39:15,020 --> 00:39:16,340
What’s the use?

876
00:39:16,350 --> 00:39:17,690
No one would like to look.

877
00:39:17,700 --> 00:39:20,220
I would like to. I like it so much.

878
00:39:24,430 --> 00:39:26,040
Be serious.

879
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:27,680
OK.

880
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:30,360
Put performers aside.

881
00:39:30,450 --> 00:39:32,700
But you know how Shang Xirui

882
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:34,210
bullied Jiang Mengping.

883
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,460
How come you still

884
00:39:35,470 --> 00:39:36,830
open a theater for him?

885
00:39:36,930 --> 00:39:39,190
It’s not only for him.

886
00:39:39,470 --> 00:39:41,360
I think Peking opera is an art.

887
00:39:41,630 --> 00:39:43,280
So I want to do a good thing.

888
00:39:44,350 --> 00:39:46,920
Only good people deserve good things.

889
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:48,630
Is Shang Xirui a good man?

890
00:39:48,830 --> 00:39:50,560
He’s full of tricks.

891
00:39:51,150 --> 00:39:53,100
He also asked actors to

892
00:39:53,130 --> 00:39:54,310
accost your younger sister.

893
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:55,820
How come you are still in a dream?

894
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:59,400
Who? Accosted Chacha’er?

895
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:01,650
No way.

896
00:40:01,750 --> 00:40:02,780
I said the truth.

897
00:40:03,580 --> 00:40:06,170
They tricked the brother,

898
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:08,070
and now they target the sister.

899
00:40:10,270 --> 00:40:12,140
Shang Xirui

900
00:40:12,170 --> 00:40:13,600
will destroy our family.

901
00:40:19,640 --> 00:40:21,790
You can’t even get a concubine from the troupe.

902
00:40:22,110 --> 00:40:23,510
Why don’t you feel them dirty?

903
00:40:51,140 --> 00:40:52,960
A dirty performer

904
00:40:53,250 --> 00:40:54,340
went to our back garden

905
00:40:54,350 --> 00:40:55,910
secretly in the morning,

906
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,920
and also molest my young sister.

907
00:40:58,460 --> 00:41:00,540
Did he try to steal things

908
00:41:00,550 --> 00:41:01,920
or the lady?

909
00:41:02,390 --> 00:41:04,230
What else would a performer do

910
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,860
in my mansion without invitation?

911
00:41:06,220 --> 00:41:08,040
Fish begins to stink at the head.

912
00:41:08,110 --> 00:41:09,180
So the young performers

913
00:41:09,190 --> 00:41:10,340
won’t be good.

914
00:41:11,070 --> 00:41:12,640
They may commit something worse than stealing,

915
00:41:12,710 --> 00:41:14,760
like murder or arson.

916
00:41:15,430 --> 00:41:17,060
Take your little thief

917
00:41:17,070 --> 00:41:18,020
back.

918
00:41:31,460 --> 00:41:32,790
From now on,

919
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:35,340
I won’t be with you.

920
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:37,670
Take care of yourself.

921
00:41:40,670 --> 00:41:43,760
As opera performers, youth is what we live on.

922
00:41:44,750 --> 00:41:46,540
But youth fleets.

923
00:41:49,150 --> 00:41:51,960
This is the best result that I can get.

924
00:41:52,910 --> 00:41:54,480
My fate can’t be changed.

925
00:41:57,470 --> 00:42:00,000
You must seize chances

926
00:42:00,610 --> 00:42:02,110
to live a better life.

927
00:42:27,310 --> 00:42:30,020
The day breaks from the drums.

928
00:42:30,240 --> 00:42:32,950
Spring comes to Warmness Palace.

929
00:42:34,490 --> 00:42:35,310
What are you laughing for?

930
00:42:35,890 --> 00:42:39,160
Shijiu. Did you make a mistake?

931
00:42:39,290 --> 00:42:41,170
The lines are weird.

932
00:42:41,180 --> 00:42:42,590
Do you know opera?

933
00:42:43,610 --> 00:42:46,990
It’s not “the day breaks”, but “the sun rises”.

934
00:42:47,300 --> 00:42:49,630
Leader said the punishment is a slap

935
00:42:49,980 --> 00:42:51,650
if we sing one word wrong.

936
00:42:52,190 --> 00:42:53,960
I’ll give you a slap now.

937
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:55,490
Focus on your butt.

938
00:43:00,430 --> 00:43:02,180
Mr. Du, you are the writer.

939
00:43:02,270 --> 00:43:03,790
Did I say it wrong?

940
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:04,740
As long as

941
00:43:04,750 --> 00:43:06,630
the line hears smooth.

942
00:43:07,690 --> 00:43:09,200
Do you think it’s smooth?

943
00:43:09,390 --> 00:43:10,740
Here. Read it again.

944
00:43:11,690 --> 00:43:13,670
The one who decides it

945
00:43:13,730 --> 00:43:14,930
is still our leader.

946
00:43:15,730 --> 00:43:18,780
Good. You are all earlier than me.

947
00:43:19,430 --> 00:43:20,820
Leader, good morning.

948
00:43:20,830 --> 00:43:21,980
Today, we’ll select the performers

949
00:43:21,990 --> 00:43:23,230
for Zhao Feiyan.

950
00:43:23,240 --> 00:43:24,130
Everyone works hard

951
00:43:24,140 --> 00:43:25,500
for it.
